headline: Popular 49-year-old pizza chain files for Chapter 11 bankruptcy
summary: The pizza restaurant industry is one of the most competitive dining sectors in the U.S., with two pizza giants ranking among the Top 8 of all fast-food chains based on locations in 2025. Domino's had the sixth-most number of locations with 7,014, behind Subway (19,502), Starbucks (16,935), ...
